图片描述：

所提供的宣传艺术作品（watermarked_img_13932547036372967481.png）展示了位于德国科隆的独立网络项目KWD（kwd.omg.lol）的官方公告横幅，庆祝其获得omg.lol的官方赞助。作品采用充满活力、细节丰富的漫画风格，视觉上传达了整个#KWDCORE网络的创意、包容和亚文化特质。

整体构图直接创意性地致敬了omg.lol的官方主页标志（image(2).png）。它采用了标志性的浅蓝色天空、微笑的粉色心形、蓝色小鸟，以及由房屋、风力发电机、天文台和彩虹旗组成的多彩矢量天际线。顶部居中醒目地呈现了3D风格字体，写着“KWD. OMG. LOL”。

这幅图的最大亮点：画面中的四个漫画角色并非不同的团队成员，而是代表了这位科隆项目创始人的不同化身和主题侧面——他是一位神经多样性作家兼包容性媒体活动家，也为包容性媒体项目Alexianer-Start-XBlog撰稿。作为统一的视觉纽带，几乎所有角色都拥有鲜艳的莫西干发型，象征着深厚的朋克与独立亚文化根基：

Doc Köllewood（嘻哈/都市生活）：这个化身身穿街头服饰，头戴黑色帽子、墨镜，挂着金链，代表都市文化和音乐亚文化。其朋克根源通过醒目的火红与橙黄渐变莫西干发型得以突出。

Sean Köllewood（电影/剧集/游戏）：戴着眼镜和紫色莫西干发型，这个角色代表对极客文化、动漫和游戏的热情。他手持发光的蓝色光剑，两侧是流行文化标志，如TARDIS和暴风兵头盔。

Seb aka San-Dre（政治/社会/科学）：这个形象不戴眼镜，以引人注目的绿与蓝绿色渐变莫西干发型脱颖而出。他手持一本名为《Wissenschaft》（科学）的书，周围环绕着欧盟旗帜等符号，代表社会评论、技术和环保意识。

Basti aka MrSeAnLan（梗图与趣闻）：创始人的幽默面。戴着绿色青蛙帽和未来风格遮阳镜，这个形象代表生活方式、网络亚文化和表情包。

聚焦包容与社群价值：
横幅下部致力于阐述项目的核心理念。在标语“Gemeinsam für eine bessere Community！”（一起打造更美好的社群！）下，创始人通过不同的图标强化了其核心使命——尊重与宽容、无障碍与包容、知识分享以及神经多样性意识。

链接、支持与版权信息：
项目支持选项：

加入社群（推荐链接）：home.omg.lol/referred-by/kwd

官方omg.lol赞助信息：home.omg.lol/info/sponsorships

通过小费罐支持：home.omg.lol/tip-jar

图片来源与版权声明：
所提供的媒体素材的布局和设计语言深受omg.lol平台原创作品（艺术家：@andycarolan）的启发。最终构图及KWD化身的视觉渲染是代表项目创始人使用生成式人工智能（AI）创作的。媒体机构可以自由使用此图像素材进行关于KWD社群和包容项目的编辑报道，前提是给予相关方适当署名。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Here is the detailed, inclusive alt text in English for your new banner (watermarked_img_11921035114264003900.png). You can copy and paste this directly into Mastodon's image description field when you upload your header banner:

Alternative Text:

A vibrant, highly detailed comic-style banner for the web community &amp;quot;KWD. OMG. LOL&amp;quot; set against the scenic skyline of Cologne, Germany, featuring the Cologne Cathedral, the Rhine riverbank, a bridge, and a passing boat. At the top, the bold 3D text reads &amp;quot;KWD. OMG. LOL&amp;quot;, accompanied by the web address &amp;quot;kwd.omg.lol&amp;quot; and the tagline &amp;quot;The Fun Web Community&amp;quot;. A cheerful pink heart with a face and a smiling blue bird float in the sky.

Four distinct comic characters—representing different alter egos of the project’s founder—are lined up horizontally in the center, each with an designated nameplate and their thematic focus:

Doc Köllewood (Hiphop / Urban Life): A light-skinned man sporting a striking fiery red-and-orange gradient mohawk, sunglasses, a black cap with &amp;quot;KWD&amp;quot; written on it, a black hoodie, and a thick gold chain while holding a microphone.

Sean Köllewood (Movies / Series / Games): A man with glasses and a vibrant purple mohawk wearing a black &amp;quot;KWD&amp;quot; hoodie. He holds a glowing blue lightsaber and a gaming controller, flanked by pop culture nods including a TARDIS, a Stormtrooper helmet, a Pokéball, and a Minecraft block.

Seb aka San-Dre (Politics / Science / Society): A man without glasses showcasing a bright green-and-turquoise gradient mohawk. He holds a book titled &amp;quot;Wissenschaft&amp;quot; (Science), with an EU flag, a globe, and the scales of justice behind him, underneath a speech bubble that reads &amp;quot;Shaping the Future&amp;quot;.

Basti aka MrSeAnLan (Shitposts / Entertainment / Memes &amp;amp; Anecdotes): A joyful character wearing a green frog hood and futuristic, silver shader/visor glasses. He holds a smartphone and a sign reading &amp;quot;Memes 4 Life&amp;quot;. Beside him are a rainbow, a laughing poop emoji, and a small white cat.

At the bottom, a white information bar is labeled &amp;quot;Together for a Better Community!&amp;quot; outlining four core community values with descriptive icons: &amp;quot;Respect &amp;amp; Tolerance&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Share Knowledge &amp;amp; Learn from Each Other&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Have Fun &amp;amp; Stay Positive&amp;quot;, and &amp;quot;Celebrate Diversity &amp;amp; Be Inclusive&amp;quot;. The banner concludes at the very bottom with a purple stripe stating &amp;quot;Kwd joins omg.lol – The Fun Web Community.&amp;quot;" height="683" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/kwd/6a18adec33e98.jpg" width="1024"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://kwd.some.pics"&gt;@kwd&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 May 2026 21:04:46 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>胡椒树</title><link>https://some.pics/6a18a9323d2bb</link><description>&lt;p&gt;胡椒树&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Bountiful thin green peppertree leave with red pepper berries against a blue sky." height="3024" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/macmanx/6a18a9323d2bb.jpg" width="4032"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://macmanx.some.pics"&gt;@macmanx&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 May 2026 20:44:38 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a189c8c9260e</link><description>&lt;p&gt;新 #vintage #眼镜！同时，首次适应 #渐进镜片👓 😁&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="A close-up selfie of a person with silver-framed, clear cat-eye glasses. They are smiling warmly at the camera, wearing a purple t-shirt and a delicate necklace. Bright green trees and a blue sky are visible in the soft-focus background.

